### üåç Multi-Modal Compatibility

**Legacy Support:**
- SMS/USSD for feature phones (India, Africa, rural areas)
- Voice-based IVR systems (illiterate populations)
- Physical paper vouchers (no-digital communities)
- Radio-based verification (disaster zones)

**Current Stack:**
- Progressive Web Apps (offline-first)
- QR codes + cryptographic hashing
- Real-time API synchronization
- Responsive web design

**Future Vision:**
- AR glasses with spatial vouchers
- Biometric verification (iris, fingerprint, voice)
- IoT water dispensers with auto-reporting
- Satellite-based location verification
- AI-powered fraud detection (privacy-preserving)
- Brain-computer interfaces for accessibility

